00:11.720 --> 00:15.473
Mr. Reilly. You might want to get
a little Alzheimer's of your own.

00:15.473 --> 00:17.392
- Excuse me?
- Jeannie's happy here.

00:17.892 --> 00:19.477
Now you have to be happy too.

00:19.477 --> 00:21.479
You telling me, forget about my wife?

00:23.231 --> 00:24.315
Survivor's guilt.

00:24.482 --> 00:26.860
You're like the
second person, like,

00:27.652 --> 00:30.363
recently that's mentioned that to me.

00:30.363 --> 00:32.032
- How's it with Natalie?
- I don't know, man.

00:32.032 --> 00:34.701
I think she might have another guy
she's living with on the hook.

00:34.701 --> 00:36.411
This is my big brother, Rich.

00:37.162 --> 00:38.204
Rich, this is Franco.

00:38.204 --> 00:39.372
How's it going?

00:39.497 --> 00:42.042
If you want to run,
do it now and get it over with.

00:42.625 --> 00:44.544
No, sweetheart, not me. I'm sticking.

00:44.544 --> 00:47.047
This is a transfer. What is this, a joke?

00:47.213 --> 00:49.257
You work all day with a guy,
you think you know him.

00:49.257 --> 00:51.051
There's more about Mike
that you don't know.

00:51.051 --> 00:52.135
Oh, yeah, like what?

00:52.135 --> 00:53.678
He's playing for the other team, dude.

00:53.803 --> 00:56.306
- Mike's gay.
- Yeah, tell me something I don't know.

00:57.849 --> 01:00.185
Oh, you mean gay gay.

01:00.185 --> 01:01.644
I got this cousin down in Florida.

01:01.644 --> 01:03.521
He's got this fishing boat. Charter boat.

01:03.521 --> 01:04.939
Makes a whole boat load of money.

01:05.190 --> 01:07.901
Got a first mate, the guy got married,
he's not coming back.

01:07.901 --> 01:10.904
He asked me if I was interested,
I said no. Now I'm thinking yes.

01:10.904 --> 01:12.655
I think the crew might be breaking up.

01:12.781 --> 01:13.782
- What?
- Yeah.

01:14.074 --> 01:15.784
That's why I'm here, Mr. Gavin,

01:15.784 --> 01:18.661
to ask you, most sincerely, for...

01:19.537 --> 01:21.331
for your daughter Maggie's
hand in marriage.

01:21.664 --> 01:22.874
Are you retarded?

01:23.083 --> 01:24.084
Let me help you.

01:24.084 --> 01:27.670
I can do that. I can make a better life
for the both of us.

01:27.670 --> 01:30.590
I have all that widow money
just sitting in the bank.

01:30.590 --> 01:33.343
All I have to do is call the bank,

01:33.885 --> 01:38.848
and the next day, I would have
a check for $3.1 million.

01:38.848 --> 01:40.767
