from somebody else.

01:41.976 --> 01:43.144
Janet's pregnant.

01:44.854 --> 01:46.022
Congratulations.

02:05.542 --> 02:06.751
Stack?

02:14.551 --> 02:15.760
Stack?

02:19.222 --> 02:20.265
Listen to me.

02:21.057 --> 02:22.308
Think about the cabin.

02:23.560 --> 02:26.187
Up at the cabin with Deb and the kids.

02:31.192 --> 02:32.235
What?

02:38.867 --> 02:39.951
- Hi.
- Hey.

02:40.076 --> 02:42.620
Hey. How's he doing? Hello.

02:42.620 --> 02:43.913
- How are you?
- How is he?

02:43.913 --> 02:45.498
- He's good. He's good.
- Good.

02:45.623 --> 02:48.001
- Here, I brought you some coffee.
- Let me give you a hand.

02:48.001 --> 02:50.003
- Thank you.
- How are the kids doing?

02:50.503 --> 02:52.797
I don't want them to see him like this.

02:52.797 --> 02:54.883
You know, the older ones,
they're gonna get upset.

02:54.883 --> 02:58.761
The younger ones, I don't know
the mental damage it's gonna do.

02:58.887 --> 03:00.763
- You know I'm right, right?
- Yes.

03:00.763 --> 03:04.517
The Yankees, they beat Boston last night,
and the boys, they were all excited.

03:04.517 --> 03:08.646
Like I could really give a shit.
It reminded me of him, you know.

03:08.646 --> 03:10.982
- Yeah.
- How much he hates the Red Sox.

03:11.357 --> 03:15.361
When they came back and won that four
and then they won that world series.

03:15.570 --> 03:16.988
- Remember?
- Yeah.

03:17.155 --> 03:19.115
Such a softie.

03:19.449 --> 03:21.951
He rooted for the Red Sox
in that world series

03:21.951 --> 03:23.494
because he felt bad for the fans.

03:23.703 --> 03:25.538
You know, for all the years they lost.

03:25.538 --> 03:26.706
Right.

03:26.706 --> 03:29.834
Oh... that's what I love about him.

03:31.044 --> 03:36.758
He had this, um, this survival thing.
This, uh... this guilt.

03:37.383 --> 03:38.468
You heard of it?

03:39.469 --> 03:41.596
A couple guys in...

03:43.431 --> 03:45.934
the firehouse were talking about it, yeah.

03:45.934 --> 03:48.019
Yeah? Oh, that's better.

03:49.729 --> 03:51.731
Go. You look exhausted.

03:52.523 --> 03:54.275
- You sure? 'Cause...
- Yeah. Really.

03:54.275 --> 03:55.735
My sister's coming.

03:55.735 --> 03:58.404
His mom and dad.
I'm gonna be fine. Really, go.

03:58.404 --> 04:00.073
'Cause I can stay until they get...

04:00.073 --> 04:01.866
It's fine. Thank you.

04:01.866 --> 04:05.954
Honestly, you have been amazing.
You've been a rock through all this.

04:05.954 --> 04:07.038
Thank you.

04:07.413 --> 04:11.709
Really, thank you for taking,
taking time off from your kids

04:11.709 --> 04:13.169
and your family. Thank you.

04:13.378 --> 04:15.505
Just doing what he would've done for me.

04:15.797 --> 04:17.257
You are amazing. Thank you.

04:17.799 --> 04:19.217
And please tell Janet I said

04:19.217 --> 04:21.844
I really appreciate
her letting you do this for us.

04:22.387 --> 04:23.388
- Okay.
- Okay.

04:23.388 --> 04:25.098
All right, see you.

04:25.098 --> 04:26.391
Bye.

04:38.194 --> 04:40.571
- Hello?
- Hey. I, uh...

04:41.990 --> 04:43.241
I gotta see you.

04:43.408 --> 04:44.909
<i>For what? You already know the news.</i>

04:47.036 --> 04:48.788
I want to see you face to face, okay?

04:49.205 --> 04:51.666
You owe me that, at least,
don't you think?

04:52.041 --> 04:53.626
It's not gonna change anything.

04:53.960 --> 04:55.795
Okay, I need to...

04:56.170 --> 04:57.338
<i>To what?</i>

04:57.338 --> 05:02.051
I want to set up some rules. Figure out
how we're gonna explain everything to...

05:02.385 --> 05:05.680
everybody. Including him, okay?

05:06.306 --> 05:07.390
I mean...

05:07.807 --> 05:10.810
This family's screwed up, and now
it's about to get more screwed up.

05:10.810 --> 05:13.938
I think you and I should have
our stories straight, don't you think?

05:14.397 --> 05:15.732
Okay. When?

05:18.568 --> 05:20.611
How about tomorrow. Like 6:00?

05:20.903 --> 05:24.157
He gets home at 6:30. Do not be late.

05:33.791 --> 05:37.045
<i>On another day
C'mon, c'mon</i>

05:37.045 --> 05:40.340
<i>With these ropes I tied
Can we do no wrong?</i>

05:40.340 --> 05:43.551
<i>Now we grieve 'cause now is gone</i>

05:43.551 --> 05:46.721
<i>Things were good when we were young</i>

05:46.721 --> 05:49.891
<i>With my teeth locked down
I could see the blood</i>

05:49.891 --> 05:53.353
