05:53.353 --> 05:56.439
<i>Now we grieve 'cause now is gone</i>

05:56.439 --> 05:59.609
<i>Things were good when we were young</i>

05:59.609 --> 06:02.779
<i>-Is it safe to say?
- C'mon, c'mon</i>

06:02.779 --> 06:06.115
