- C'mon, c'mon</i>

06:09.369 --> 06:12.789
<i>C'mon, c'mon
C'mon, c'mon</i>

06:21.881 --> 06:23.216
What are you doing?

06:23.758 --> 06:27.136
Well, I know this is your regular schedule
nowadays, and I didn't wanna

06:27.136 --> 06:29.055
