to either one of them, so...

06:32.183 --> 06:34.769
Yeah. Brutal up there.

06:34.769 --> 06:36.020
I know.

06:36.896 --> 06:37.939
What's this?

06:37.939 --> 06:41.818
Oh, well, so Damien has been after me
to get him a car 'cause, you know,

06:41.818 --> 06:43.653
he wants a ride, he wants his freedom,

06:43.653 --> 06:45.363
and so, I came up with this.

06:45.363 --> 06:48.116
You need some cheering up,
and I'll be damned if I'm gonna let him

06:48.116 --> 06:50.952
bash around town
in a brand-new vehicle. So,

06:50.952 --> 06:53.454
I will trade you this
for that piece of shit,

06:53.454 --> 06:55.790
and he can do whatever
the hell he wants to with it.

06:56.207 --> 06:57.375
This is mine.

06:57.542 --> 07:00.211
It's a Cadillac. Take it.

07:00.211 --> 07:02.922
- Take it, take it, take it, take it.
- I smell a rat.

07:02.922 --> 07:05.299
No, no, no. No rat. No rat. No.

07:05.299 --> 07:09.178
Yeah. This has nothing whatsoever
to do with what we talked about before?

07:09.178 --> 07:10.513
You can take the truck.

07:10.930 --> 07:13.349
And believe me, if you decide

07:13.349 --> 07:15.351
that you don't want to
run away with me and

07:15.726 --> 07:19.522
