and all that junk, then it's okay.

07:19.522 --> 07:22.108
It's really okay. You can keep
the truck. Yay!

07:28.948 --> 07:31.868
Oh, well... it's nice.

07:31.868 --> 07:33.870
- It's fully loaded.
- Yeah.

07:34.412 --> 07:36.205
- It's a Cadillac.
- It's a pick-up truck.

07:37.123 --> 07:39.584
And you know, you giving him
something like this,

07:39.584 --> 07:41.961
that's sending completely
the wrong message.

07:41.961 --> 07:45.214
Right. Not to mention totally dangerous.
It's got a V-10 in it.

07:45.214 --> 07:47.133
That's a... deathtrap.

07:47.133 --> 07:48.885
- For a teenager.
- I know.

07:48.885 --> 07:49.969
Oh, yeah.

07:50.094 --> 07:51.304
Let me see a minute.

07:53.890 --> 07:55.349
- It's big, huh?
- Yeah.

07:55.349 --> 07:56.893
Big shit.

07:57.727 --> 07:58.853
It smells pretty, right?

07:58.853 --> 08:00.521
It still has the paper stuff on the floor.

08:00.521 --> 08:01.647
I know.

08:01.647 --> 08:03.691
Let's see what it sounds like.

08:05.902 --> 08:08.321
No, wait, wait. Don't you wanna
have a breaky or something?

08:08.321 --> 08:09.530
I can't, sweetheart. I'm late.

08:09.530 --> 08:11.282
- All right, okay.
- All right.

08:11.282 --> 08:13.451
- Yey. See you.
- Bye. See you.

08:20.208 --> 08:21.334
He's retarded?

08:21.876 --> 08:22.960
Kind of.

08:23.419 --> 08:26.672
Well, like, <i>Rain Man</i> retarded, or,
you know, Paris Hilton retarded?

08:26.672 --> 08:28.674
He's functional, all right, like Paris.

08:28.674 --> 08:32.053
He can go to the bathroom on his own,
which I'm assuming Paris can do.

08:32.470 --> 08:33.679
He's pretty good with numbers.

08:33.679 --> 08:37.225
I'm not saying the guy can count
toothpicks off the floor or anything.

08:37.391 --> 08:39.810
But, you know, then he eats things.

08:39.977 --> 08:42.230
Well, hey, hey, now.
There's nothing retarded about that.

08:42.230 --> 08:45.399
No, I'm not talking about food things,
Lou, I'm talking about actual things.

08:45.399 --> 08:47.151
All right, shit that's laying
around the room.

08:47.151 --> 08:50.488
Checkers, paper clips. Erasers, pen caps.

08:50.488 --> 08:52.573
Guy's lower intestine
must have a steel lining.

08:52.573 --> 08:54.408
You know how they
talk about retards having,

08:54.408 --> 08:55.743
what is it called, retard strength?

08:55.743 --> 08:57.453
What are you looking at me for?

08:57.912 --> 09:00.039
You know, maybe that's what
Richie the retard has.

09:00.039 --> 09:02.625
He's got all of his powers
concentrated in his digestive tract.

09:02.750 --> 09:05.461
The thing is, I really wanna
make a good impression with Nat.

09:05.461 --> 09:07.171
I was thinking I'd take him
to a ball game.

09:07.171 --> 09:08.881
Oh, yeah. That's a nice gesture.

09:08.881 --> 09:10.841
Give you a chance to bond.
That would be a good idea.

09:10.967 --> 09:12.843
Should work out real nice.

09:12.843 --> 09:15.596
Assuming, he doesn't eat the tickets
before you reach the gate.

09:44.292 --> 09:45.793
Not today, asshole.

09:48.546 --> 09:50.256
- It's incredible.
- Is it an Escalade?

09:50.256 --> 09:51.799
It's an Escalade pick-up.

09:51.799 --> 09:53.634
Cadillac goes white trash.

09:53.634 --> 09:55.261
- What?
- Nothing. How'd you get it?

09:55.261 --> 09:56.512
I decided to treat myself.

09:56.512 --> 09:59.932
Listen, it came with everything. It came
with a V-10, which is unheard of.

09:59.932 --> 10:01.642
They only made like
2,000 of those this year.

10:01.642 --> 10:03.603
It came with bucket seats,
it came with AC.

10:03.603 --> 10:05.354
Did it come with a chauffeur?

10:05.479 --> 10:06.731
Hey, hey, wait a minute.

10:06.731 --> 10:08.316
God damn it! That's my truck!

10:08.858 --> 10:09.942
Hey!

10:10.401 --> 10:11.485
Shit!

10:15.406 --> 10:17.241
Well, it looks awfully nice from the back.

10:18.784 --> 10:20.870
Okay, yeah. Great. Thank you.

10:21.746 --> 10:23.706
Cops are on the case.
What's the city coming to?

10:23.706 --> 10:25.166
Twelve minutes, I owned that vehicle.

10:25.166 --> 10:27.543
Need I remind you how far
uptown our house is located.

10:28.127 --> 10:30.421
Nice to know you haven't lost touch
with your inner racist, Lou.

10:30.421 --> 10:32.298
Franco, I'm just stating
a geographical fact.

10:32.298 --> 10:34.508
I gave my other piece of shit to Damien.

10:34.508 --> 10:36.636
So it's gonna be at least three days

10:36.636 --> 10:38.763
before the cops find the Escalade,
or what's left of it.

10:38.763 --> 10:40.681
You're worried about
getting to work, take the bus.

10:40.806 --> 10:41.807
Yeah, the subway.

10:41.807 --> 10:43.434
Yeah, take the subway. I live in Brooklyn.

10:43.434 --> 10:45.144
I can't be stuck on the train
for 45 minutes

10:45.144 --> 10:47.938
in between Dom DeLuise and Ruben Studdard.
I'll take a hostage.

10:47.938 --> 10:49.899
Wait, Ruben Studdard,
that's the gay guy, right?

10:49.899 --> 10:52.777
No, no, no. Ruben Studdard
was the fat guy. Clay Aiken's the fag.

10:52.777 --> 10:54.945
Clay Aiken ain't a fag.
He's just not talented.

10:54.945 --> 10:57.281
- I should know, I voted for the guy.
- Guys.

10:57.281 --> 10:59.283
Mike, they didn't
mean anything by it.

10:59.283 --> 11:01.202
Sorry, Mike. I forgot you were gay.

11:01.202 --> 11:03.746
You know, I just got finished
being ragged on for being the probie,

11:03.746 --> 11:05.039
now I got to deal with this shit.

11:05.998 --> 11:07.083
