This is depressing, Theodore.

11:50.126 --> 11:52.420
I guess you're right.

11:54.255 --> 11:56.674
God damn it, probie. How about knocking.

11:56.674 --> 11:59.135
Here's my transfer form, chief.
I want out.

11:59.927 --> 12:02.012
From what I hear, you're already out.

12:02.304 --> 12:05.224
Thanks for the insurance policy,
now put my transfer through,

12:05.224 --> 12:07.768
or I dial up my union rep
and tell him what you just said.

12:15.943 --> 12:18.946
Hey, Nat. Are you doing okay?

12:19.405 --> 12:21.282
I am now. You?

12:21.282 --> 12:22.700
I miss you.

12:23.451 --> 12:24.785
You're sweet.

12:24.785 --> 12:28.456
Listen, Nat, I was thinking, if you need
to get a little work done tomorrow,

12:28.456 --> 12:30.332
I could maybe take Richard out.

12:30.332 --> 12:31.459
Watch him for a little bit.

12:31.459 --> 12:33.043
