- Yeah, yeah.

12:33.043 --> 12:34.170
Take a sick day.

12:34.170 --> 12:36.130
Friend of mine's got box seats
at Yankee Stadium.

12:36.130 --> 12:38.716
That's so nice, but, um,

12:39.717 --> 12:42.678
