from Yankee Stadium.

12:42.678 --> 12:43.763
Really?

12:43.763 --> 12:48.184
He's apparently the only one in New York
to ever toss racial slurs at Derek Jeter.

12:49.310 --> 12:52.229
Well, what about a, I don't know,
a tour of the firehouse?

12:52.229 --> 12:53.314
Richard might like that.

12:53.314 --> 12:55.065
Oh, he would love that.

12:55.065 --> 12:59.195
